			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Go to SCL_Main_A / Colony&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to any of the intellect devourers. After they are done speaking, the interacting player will say this line once (non-repeatable)." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The party interacts with any of the intellect devourers in the Colony, and says this line after the intellect devourers are done speaking. They say this only once.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Intellect devourer lines are in: COL_GEN_AD_IntellectDevourer_1cde5899-11a9-e82f-a49d-f038a554490e&#xD;&#xA;They're just generic, neutral lines." />
